          <h5>Share</h5>
          <p>Share your customized app trough the provided link.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="work_card card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511988617509-a57c8a288659?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1351&q=80" class="card-img-top" alt="Connect">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5>Connect</h5>
